  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HOPSHOT is a difficult precision platformer about a lonely gay frog with a gun. Just like in real life, frogs can only move by hopping and shooting their pistols.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plan your routes, discover the secrets, and destroy anything in your way to make your Wish come true! Or fail and join the lost souls at the bottom of The Wishing Well for eternity. Strategy & planning ahead are key!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3 Controls: Jumping, Aiming, & Shooting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Secret frog colors and hats to discover!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495790/extras/cf5b675dec45c375032d37a9c2bd2e04.poster.avif?t=1760561099\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495790/extras/cf5b675dec45c375032d37a9c2bd2e04.webm?t=1760561099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Changing trajectory Mid-air!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495790/extras/fabd02343dde4335c3c3415b37e646f9.poster.avif?t=1760561099\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495790/extras/fabd02343dde4335c3c3415b37e646f9.webm?t=1760561099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-save after every jump!<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495790/extras/47b4bb894c63d685cc5ac1f70ef883f7.poster.avif?t=1760561099\" width=800 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3495790/extras/47b4bb894c63d685cc5ac1f70ef883f7.webm?t=1760561099\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
